# 🐍 Snake Game

This Snake Game was created with the help of AI as part of my learning journey. I used AI to understand concepts, improve the code, and learn how game development works while building the project myself.

## Features
- 🎮 Classic Snake Game
- 🍎 Random food generation
- 📈 Score tracking
- ⌨️ Keyboard controls
- 🎨 Simple user interface

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Purpose
This project was built for learning web development and JavaScript game development. AI was used as a learning assistant to understand concepts, debug code, and improve the implementation.

## How to Run
1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Open the src folder.
3. Open index.html in your browser.

